    "text": [
        "Dear Sir/Madam",
        "I am writing regarding the contributions you are seeking from the readers for an article called 'the book that influenced me most\", that you are planning to publish in next month\u2019s featured edition. I would like to be a part of this article regarding a book that has had a great impact on my career.",
        "This book is called A complete balance by Hannah, which mainly focuses on work-life balance in today\u2019s world and why it is important. It introduces some techniques that can help an individual to prioritize the work and personal activities leading to an equal balance.",
        "I often struggled to find time for my personal life after work and this book has introduced me to the areas where I can work to balance my professional and personal life. Ever since I read this book, I have been able to manage my time in a better way.",
        "I think this would be an influential book for many as today a lot of people are struggling with this issue. I recommended it to some of my friends and they had similar benefits as  mine. So I believe including this in your article will help thousands of readers to overcome the problem.",
        "Yours faithfully",
        "Hansy"
